      <title>特朗普威胁终止电动汽车税收抵免，美国汽车销量年底获提振</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/car-sales-get-year-end-boost-from-trump-threat-to-end-ev-tax-credit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普威胁终止对电动汽车的税收抵免，这提振了第四季度的电动汽车销量，在经历了令人失望的一年之后，为美国汽车制造商提供了急需的提振。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/car-sales-get-year-end-boost-from-trump-threat-to-end-ev-tax-credit</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
